book-text-ghostbar-paper = [head=2]Welcome to the Ghost Bar![/head]
       ———————————————————————————

    You died to some unfortunate event or chose to hangout here! HGI welcomes you to the ghost bar.

    Either way, you chose to move on to the afterlife.

    Please treat this role, and station, as you would just being a regular Ghost. You may talk about all current round events without the need for LOOC, and you remember everything from your previous life.

    DO NOT attack others, start fights, or attempt to break the station. If you see anyone doing this, please Ahelp so admins can handle it.

    Also, if you decide to leave the bar, you DO NOT remember anything from being here, or your life before it.
